00:00:35.789 --> 00:00:37.409
We're going to cut it into squares.

00:00:37.409 --> 00:00:41.839
The easiest way I find is just to cut it with
a pizza slicer, and so you cut them into two

00:00:41.839 --> 00:00:42.839
different sizes.

